{"tid":2412541,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"愛沙尼亞對外情報局發表年度報告 警告“北京主導的沉默世界”  研究員: 最擔心世界秩序被瓦解","createTime":"2021-02-18T05:45:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T17:29:37.000Z","uid":39464,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ff00db2cb28a4528e552af9590579818b2f34e39","tid":2412541,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/d70d921c-713b-11eb-b177-005056a964fe/w:980/p:16x9/Capture-348.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.rfi.fr%2Fmedia%2Fdisplay%2Fd70d921c-713b-11eb-b177-005056a964fe%2Fw%3A980%2Fp%3A16x9%2FCapture-348.webp&h=02b7f9af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 愛沙尼亞對外情報局（V&auml;lisluureamet）2月17日發表了《國際安全與愛沙尼亞2021》年度報告。報告描繪了一幅中國試圖壓制批評，並主導愛沙尼亞和其他民主國家的關鍵技術的局面。<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n愛沙尼亞對外情報局在這份82頁的文件中，於末尾花了9頁的篇幅來描述&ldquo;來自中國正在增加的壓力&rdquo;。報告稱，&ldquo;貫徹中國的外交政策理論，或者說建立'共同命運共同體'，將導致一個由北京主導的沉默世界。面對與西方日益加劇的對抗，中國的主要目標是在美國和歐洲之間製造分裂。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n報告中有關中國的部分強調，北京通過經濟槓桿、監視海外中國公民和培養當地精英，在西方進行影響力行動的能力越來越強。報告還警告說，中國領導層 &ldquo;有一個明確的目標，就是讓世界依賴中國技術&rdquo;，並提到了5G製造商華為和北鬥導航系統。<br />\n<br />\n位於愛沙尼亞首都塔林的，國際防務與安全中心愛沙尼亞外交政策研究所的研究員尤里斯（Frank J&uuml;ris）說，<strong>&ldquo;愛沙尼亞最擔心的是，30年前讓愛沙尼亞重新獲得獨立的世界秩序，以及過去30年我們參與的繁榮和發展被瓦解。&rdquo;他說，&ldquo;我們的世界秩序被瓦解了。&rdquo;</strong><br />\n<br />\n與同為歐盟成員國的德國、法國等大國相比，愛沙尼亞和捷克一樣，對北京行為的批評更加直言不諱。<strong>尤里斯稱，&ldquo;這並不是歐洲小國第一次成為先鋒，引領正確的方向。主要是歐洲小國有過對付侵略性俄羅斯的經驗</strong>，才會對其他歐洲國家警告俄羅斯政權。&rdquo;愛沙尼亞對外情報局負責人米克&bull;馬蘭(Mikk Marran)周三在推特上寫道，&ldquo;我們將繼續關注那些不遵守規則的人，並向大家通報。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB/20210217-%E6%84%9B%E6%B2%99%E5%B0%BC%E4%BA%9E%E5%B0%8D%E5%A4%96%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E5%B1%80%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%A8%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A-%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E4%B8%BB%E5%B0%8E%E7%9A%84%E6%B2%89%E9%BB%98%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%2F20210217-%25E6%2584%259B%25E6%25B2%2599%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E4%25BA%259E%25E5%25B0%258D%25E5%25A4%2596%25E6%2583%2585%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%25B1%2580%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2591%258A-%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B0%258E%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25B2%2589%25E9%25BB%2598%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOsemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=8f7bca96\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB/20210217-%E6%84%9B%E6%B2%99%E5%B0%BC%E4%BA%9E%E5%B0%8D%E5%A4%96%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E5%B1%80%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%A8%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A-%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E4%B8%BB%E5%B0%8E%E7%9A%84%E6%B2%89%E9%BB%98%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C</a>"},{"pid":"0979d86bb87ed08e98b97897e8b1ace3d6ab483d","tid":2412541,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:47:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f2ad77b36ed1e7d3198bc5c2ade754488a56b3","tid":2412541,"uid":100986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T01:50:45.000Z","msg":"拜燈:<br />\n愛沙尼亞、立陶宛和拉脫維亞不要刺激中俄"},{"pid":"cd2afa9d0019801bb9e29d1a9a1d79e00a96285d","tid":2412541,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T01:53:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8311eefbc7cc087e5d8dc93887bf56e6eb9b3478","tid":2412541,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T01:57:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf64e0b3e7e93f3a6adec7005602677cbd6b8f05","tid":2412541,"uid":114781,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":